    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.11">
<l>kuṭaintuvaṇ ṭuṇṇum tuḻāymuṭi yāṉai</l>
<l>yaṭainta teṉ kurukūrccaṭa kōpaṉ</l>
<l>miṭainta col toṭai yāyirattippat</l>
<l>tuṭaintu nōykaḷai yōṭu vikkumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These ten in the thousand of the wreath of words set close</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ from southern Kurukūr who approaches</l>
<l>the one with the Tulsi crown worked through [and] eaten by bees</l>
<l>will break [and] chase away pains.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
